capsules.title: Dear Future Me
capsules.message:
Capsulr's vault holds this note, unfolding only for you. What dreams did you chase? What lessons did you learn? I wonder how you've grown, what joys you've savored, and what challenges you've overcome.

In this moment, I'm curious about the paths taken and the person you've become. Did you stay true to your passions? Did you nurture connections that matter?

May this capsule remind you of intentions, hopes, and the journey's beauty. Here's to reflecting, growing, and embracing life's unfolding story.
